        "product_description": {
            "value": "The ASR Outdoor Universal Fit Survival Paracord Belt is the ultimate everyday carry and outdoor gear accessory for men. Crafted from 100 percent 550 paracord, this belt measures a full 52 inches in length and features a durable stainless steel buckle for a secure, reliable hold. Designed as a one-size-fits-all belt, the extra length can be tucked within your belt loops or cut to fit and singed at the ends for a clean, custom finish. With no pre-made holes, you simply slide the belt clasp through the paracord weave wherever it feels most comfortable, giving you a truly adjustable and personalized fit. Woven from strong survival cord, this belt does more than hold up your pants. In an emergency, the paracord can be unraveled to provide feet of rugged rope for camping, hiking, hunting, or survival situations. The sleek black solid color and silver buckle deliver a versatile tactical look that pairs well with casual and outdoor apparel alike. Machine washable and built to last, the ASR Outdoor Paracord Belt is an excellent gift for men who love the outdoors, EDC gear, tactical equipment, and being prepared for anything. Whether you are on the trail, at the range, or handling everyday tasks, this dependable belt combines comfort, durability, and functional survival readiness in one essential piece of gear.",
